{"tid":2250830,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩民老婆蔣麗莎新造型極顯老好驚嚇　網民：可以享用長者優惠了","createTime":"2020-10-20T11:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T14:23:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9325cb43e1928d4b49e87ae27db54caad93148e8","tid":2250830,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"現年51歲的陳浩民近年轉戰內地市場，除了主力拍劇拍電影，還進軍網上平台成為抖音網紅，孖住老婆蔣麗莎 (Lisa) 一齊帶貨做網上生意。要在抖音上做帶貨網紅，首要當然就是要夠多粉絲，陳浩民兩夫妻亦好努力去經營他們的抖音帳號，經常拍片與網民分享他的生活點滴，還有做直播跟網民聊天來吸粉。<br />\n<br />\n下個月便35歲的Lisa昨日就於抖音post了一段短片分享她的最新髮色與造型，以及預告自己即將有直播，她留言表示：「今晚直播造型提前賞析，你們給她幾分呢？」看她在鏡頭前跳住舞自拍，又舉出V字手勢樣子十分陶醉，明顯十分滿意自己的新形象。不過片中的她看來相當顯老，驟眼看像個50多歲的老太太，網民毫不留情地紛紛留言負評：「我看了個老人」、「像50多歲呀」、「怎麼一臉老態」、「可以享用長者優惠了」。"},{"pid":"57e35f18b576b3b3646756f81cde0d407c28a9fc","tid":2250830,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201020/395170293427081216297453.png/K4FQbs87Qxwc11zA0v6c41ijOxaB_Rrp6kfdROpH3UQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201020%2F395170293427081216297453.png%2FK4FQbs87Qxwc11zA0v6c41ijOxaB_Rrp6kfdROpH3UQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ab642549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201020/395170296782655488359612.png/VgU9ndj7HgzsIdHYt5BqcRvdDbUKe5kahjCHGYYwhxk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201020%2F395170296782655488359612.png%2FVgU9ndj7HgzsIdHYt5BqcRvdDbUKe5kahjCHGYYwhxk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b079c90b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201020/395170300884815872563082.png/nFtbbo98mGuS4zKmaa2pTKmHWBDcqkBAjb-2-I2_tvg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201020%2F395170300884815872563082.png%2FnFtbbo98mGuS4zKmaa2pTKmHWBDcqkBAjb-2-I2_tvg%3F